  "description": "-Game Features-\n・Blackjack Style Turn-Based Battle System\nBattles are a one-on-one turn-based system.\nWho has the closest number to 21 in their hand? They deal an attack to the opponent!\n\nThree distinctive playable characters make an appearance: The Fighter, with a head on battle-like creed; the Thief, unrivaled in sensing danger and thwarting it; and the Magician, who employs trickery at will!\nLeave your strategy to chance? Entrap the enemy with trickery? The way you enjoy is up to you, the player.\n\n\n・Diverse Array of Monsters\nSlimes, orcs, dragons, and monsters, familiar to fantasy RPGs all lurk out of the depths, one after another.\nCard hand concealing ghosts, trolls that surpass the 21-card value limit, and many more with a diverse array of skills stand in the way of the player.\nMonsters from Rideon Japan's “Adventure Bar Story” and “Mercenaries Saga” series games even make an appearance!\n\n\n・Loads of Factors to Augment, Unfolding a Blackjack Victory\nAcquire boost cards as you advance the adventure, strengthening status and learning skills.\nAbilities come along with some weapons and accessories, and at the Armory & Forge in town, synthesis can allow for unbound customization.\n\nCombining skills with abilities? This could bring to life new tactics.\nCan you traverse the untrodden dungeons? It's all up to you, the player!",
